calLineOutageDFactors

public void calLineOutageDFactors(java.lang.String contId)
                           throws ReferenceBusException,
                                  OutageConnectivityException
calculate LODF for all branches in the network with regarding to the outage branch or branches. The following are sample code to use the method // set LODF to multiple outage branch setLODFAnalysisType(LODFSenAnalysisType.MULTI_BRANCH); // define outage branches for ( outage branch ) addOutageBranch(outage branch); // calculate LODF for all branches calLineOutageDFactors(); for ( each branch) { double[] fAry = algoDsl.monitorBranch(monitor branch) .getLineOutageDFactors(); ... }

Throws:
ReferenceBusException
OutageConnectivityException
